係受害者<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T14:46:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6c2c7c20e1480d6a9650f9cf429f1e21db64262","tid":1928620,"uid":270506,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T15:07:28.000Z","msg":"明明前幾日成功吹到風叫人去twitter反制支那嘅propaganda，而家開始唔知點解spin咗去笑鬼佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />與其係度笑人串人批鬥鬼佬不如將精力擺喺批鬥中共度<br />\n<br />\n其實外國人唔係on9，而係冇接收到完整資訊至會比支共呃到<br />\n不過如果大家出力打國際戰線，俾到真相外國人嘅話，就唔會出現呢個情況<br />\n所以連衛兵們係時候要進場破壞中共嘅宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請廣傳，國際戰線最新行動如下：</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AgyJbBh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAgyJbBh.jpg&h=51f4c095&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n每日喺Twitter 各大有關Coronavirus嘅post留言要求世界各國向中國追究責任，例子如下<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/liberatehk277/status/1237229652315262976?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fliberatehk277%2Fstatus%2F1237229652315262976%3Fs%3D21&d=eokTwrWYlXUgHXHl4H%2BebWqRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=ecc698ee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fliberatehk277%2Fstatus%2F1237229652315262976%3Fs%3D21&h=e8a4756c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/liberatehk277/status/1237229652315262976?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n呢個post吸左百幾個五毛入黎洗版，證明中共而家最驚世界各國向其追責！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />各位軍曹，係時候做嘢送支共一程<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n具體做法：請定時留意NY Times，BBC，CNN等等嘅國際媒體，等到佢哋一出有關Coronavirus 嘅post嘅時候要即刻reply搶頭版，呼籲世界各國向中共同WHO追責<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CV9kdN8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCV9kdN8.jpg&h=a308a7e0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d7d3ae152ecadbdea74b0b34a35957d786e56cca","tid":1928620,"uid":107793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T15:15:26.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"bee64188a03d1fe379dd04cb11def087aa6463bc","tid":1928620,"uid":107793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T22:32:55.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"de338373c58eebf8610c81191b6629b6502c6a38","tid":1928620,"uid":288670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T22:34:56.000Z","msg":"呢幾日兒登仔又瘋狂俾五毛狗帶風向屌外國人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1928549\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1928549</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8e7a2de14587fe0fcf0f1a9c99741fea35d08918","tid":1928620,"uid":155949,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8a04cbbe059b5a3a4607707a3fb90469ff0e27b4","tid":1928620,"uid":107793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T13:19:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />近日風向係以肺炎事件鼓吹連登仔反白人，企圖破壞國際戰線同香港人形象"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T22:36:28.000Z","msg":"連登仔神早輸曬啦<br />\n成日比人帶風向<br />\n又多打手"},{"pid":"27b36036ed8f1ce70577a139a4f80dc6bc433728","tid":1928620,"uid":167394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T23:01:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27d8f4f025eb3d436ffe52a476c849b263e315e2","tid":1928620,"uid":121546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T23:06:05.000Z","msg":"其實係冇人帶風向每分每秒都講黑警同5大訴求，所以連登先變返最原始既狀況<br />\n冇得笑下台灣風化案，就笑下歐洲人唔戴口罩"},{"pid":"5140b54182e37b85688dd8a8058cf6cccd358642","tid":1928620,"uid":5103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T13:14:50.000Z"